parameters:
\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I'm sorry, Master, but I'll be more comfortable
here than at the inn~!
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Hello, Rain! I've been waiting for you!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Hello. It seems like you're not sleep-deprived
today.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Because this place has a bath and the bed is
comfortable! Thanks to that, I've been able to
make great progress!
\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>However, a little problem has come up.

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I found out the location of the fourth device.
However, it seems like it's somewhere in this town
\C[17]but I'm not sure where exactly\C[0].

\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>───So you're saying that the magic device is
somewhere inside Hakudeti!?

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Yes, probably... I think it was concealed by a
much stronger barrier than the other devices.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>However, I have no idea where it is in this town.
Even though it should be nearby, the presence of
magic energy is very faint.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I haven't gone around all of Hakudeti, but I can't
think of a place where such a device could be
hidden without being noticed...

\CE[93]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I know! If we ask the thief we caught earlier,
maybe they know something?

\OC[31]\N<Rain>Indeed...! The captain of the guards should be
interrogating them, so I'll go and confirm.

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Understood, then I will continue analyzing this
magic power and try to extract any information I
can!
Events in town have been unlocked.
'Go to the guard station and listen to what Caldo has to say'

\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It's definitely somewhere in this town, right?
Hmm...

\n<Meryl>"I'll advance the analysis of the four fragments
as much as possible before we depart, so please
make sure you get plenty of rest and be prepared,
Rain!"

\n<Meryl>"The 'Nightmare Jammer' also has high resistance
to magical power, so I think it will be useful in
battles against demons!"

\CE[77]\OC[31]\N<Rain>"Meryl, you don't look so well. Are you
feeling okay?"

\CE[93]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Now that you mention it, I might not have been
getting much sleep lately. When was the last time
I ate...?"

\CE[77]\OC[31]\N<Rain>"That's no good! You'll collapse if you keep
living like that!"

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Ahaha, I get so caught up in my research that
I... Oh, I forgot there was a really dangerous
incident before because of that..."

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>"Please be careful. And if you don't sleep and eat
properly, it will surely affect your research
too."

\CE[77]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Ha-- Finally, I've made some progress...! Now I
just need to test this medicine, make some
adjustments, and it'll be complete!"

\CE[79]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"I'm so tired... I ended up not eating or drinking
again... Rain is going to scold me."

\CE[77]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Now that I think about it, I haven't replenished
my magical energy either... I've used quite a bit
for my research, so I might be running quite
low..."

\CE[79]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Hmm... As soon as I let my guard down, I suddenly
started feeling horny... My breasts are getting
swollen...♥"
"Please! I really need it to be Meryl!!"

\CE[77]\OC[31]\N<Rain>"The Thieves' Guild 'Dark Owl' has effectively
been disbanded, so I think it's safe to go out
freely now."

\CE[93]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Thank goodness! I wasn't feeling inconvenienced
here, but I really wanted to go outside."

\CE[77]\OC[31]\N<Rain>"That's right, well done. It's really thank
goodness that nothing happened up until today."
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Meryl, I'm glad to see you're doing well.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I'm sorry for putting you in danger by asking for
your help... Did you get hurt when you were being
chased?

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I'm fine! Besides, it's not your fault! I just
thought it seemed interesting, so I asked for an
investigation.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>It's reassuring to hear you say that... I'm really
glad you're safe.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>But you were able to sense the thieves beforehand.
Did you have any information?

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I had set up a barrier around the inn just in case
something like this happened! I sensed a
suspicious presence as if we were being watched,
so I quickly escaped.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Rain, I was in such a hurry that I couldn't even
leave a proper message, but you managed to find
this place well.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>While I was investigating, the innkeeper here told
me that they were worried about you and informed
me that you were working here. I apologize for
prying into personal matters, but I didn't have
any leads...

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>That's not a problem at all! I'm not hiding
anything, after all. Besides, it would be
difficult for anyone to break in here, and having
the Boss around is reassuring. I can investigate
without any worries!

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>Oh, speaking of the investigation, did you find
the third device?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Yes, thanks to your prediction, it was indeed in
the sealed dungeon. I thoroughly destroyed it, so
there are fragments as well.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>As expected! Then let's quickly search for the
fourth device! I'll take the fragments as well!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>But, you must be tired from all that just
happened, right? You can rest for a bit before...

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>It's totally fine! Besides, those thieves are
connected to the demon lord, right? So destroying
the device should also be damaging for them.

\CE[94]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>I won't let the bad guys get away! I'll definitely
find it, so please wait for another day!
\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>─Understood. Well then, please take care of me.

\N<The man who was a neighbor at the inn>"So, your 'request' is for me to take this
medicine? What kind of medicine is it?"

\CE[77]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"It's a medicine that \C[27]increases the amount
of semen\C[0]♥"
\N<The man who was a neighbor at the inn>"What!? Why would you need such a medicine!?"

\CE[77]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"I love it when you cum inside... I want you to
cum a lot...♥ There's nothing harmful to the human
body in it, so please drink it with peace of
mind!"

\N<The man who was a neighbor at the inn>"If you say something like that, I'm going to get
super excited...! Then I'll take this and give you
lots...!!"

\N<The man who was a neighbor at the inn>"Phew... Alright, everything's ready...! I can't
hold back anymore, Meryl...!!"
\CE[77]\OC[25]\N<Meryl>"Yes♥ I also want you to do it a lot to me...♥"
